<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1' />
    <style>
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        background-color: #eef2f8;
        color: #1d1d1d;
      }

      .wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 24px 0;
      }

      .container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 620px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 18px;
        box-shadow: 0 24px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .header {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0b4f8a, #1266b5);
        color: #ffffff;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 34px 28px;
      }

      .header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 28px;
        line-height: 1.15;
      }

      .header p {
        margin: 16px 0 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
      }

      .content {
        padding: 28px;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .content h2 {
        margin: 0 0 16px;
        font-size: 22px;
        color: #173f6f;
      }

      .content p {
        margin: 14px 0;
        color: #4a4a4a;
      }

      .highlight {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 12px 18px;
        margin: 10px 0;
        background: #e8f3ff;
        color: #11427b;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        background: #1266b5;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        padding: 14px 26px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        margin: 22px 0;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 24px 28px 28px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #6b6b6b;
        border-top: 1px solid #e5e9ef;
      }

      .footer strong {
        color: #1d1d1d;
      }

      @media screen and (max-width: 520px) {
        .container {
          border-radius: 0;
        }

        .header h1 {
          font-size: 24px;
        }

        .button {
          display: block;
          text-align: center;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='wrapper'>
      <div class='container'>
        <div class='header'>
          <h1>Welcome to Marvis Health Tech</h1>
          <p>Healthcare at your fingertips, {{fullName}}.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='content'>
          <h2>Your health account is ready!</h2>
          <p>We're thrilled to have you join us. Marvis Health Tech makes it easier than ever to manage your health
            needs from the comfort of your home.</p>

          <div class='highlight'>Account ID: {{email}}</div>

          <p>You can now use our platform to:</p>
          <ul style='color: #4a4a4a; padding-left: 20px;'>
            <li>Order prescription medications and essential drugs.</li>
            <li>Book diagnostic lab tests and view results.</li>
            <li>Track your medical history and orders securely.</li>
          </ul>

          <p>If you have any questions about an order or a test, our customer support team is just a message away.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='footer'>
          <p>To your health,<br /><strong>The Marvis Health Tech Team</strong></p>
          <p><strong>Marvis Health Tech</strong> · Reliable Pharmacy & Diagnostic Services</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>